WEBVTT

00:11:27.978 --> 00:11:30.084
to people like us.

00:11:30.084 --> 00:11:32.791
(Applause)

00:11:32.791 --> 00:11:34.775
Things have come to this point

00:11:34.775 --> 00:11:37.267
because politicians in general,

00:11:37.267 --> 00:11:40.163
but especially in our countries, let's face it,

00:11:40.163 --> 00:11:42.626
think people are stupid.

00:11:42.626 --> 00:11:46.170
They take it for granted that, come what may,

00:11:46.170 --> 00:11:48.382
people have to follow them,

00:11:48.382 --> 00:11:52.476
while politics, more and more, fails to offer answers

00:11:52.476 --> 00:11:56.499
for their public concerns

00:11:56.499 --> 00:12:01.170
or the exigencies of the common people.